title: The Wonder Years - The Complete First Season [Uncut] [StarVista
description:
The Wonder Years - The Complete First Season [Uncut] [StarVista Edition]

This is the complete first season of The Wonder Years. These episodes are ripped from the StarVista edition, which is the official released of the series completely uncut. Please note- I have no control over the quality of the video, as StarVista went through great expense to get the music rights for the episodes and obviously didn't remaster the series for DVD. But, at least we get the show completely uncut as it was originally intended.

If you guys enjoy this release, please comment and I will go ahead and do other seasons. Seed for other fans please. :)
